properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Pt. St. George to Cape Mendocino CA out 10 nm
properties.headline: Hazardous Seas Warning issued January 15 at 9:27PM PST until January 16 at 4:00AM PST by NWS Eureka CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts up to 50 kt and seas
11 to 16 feet.

* WHERE...Pt St George to Cape Mendocino out 10 nm.

* WHEN...Until 4 AM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Recreational boaters should remain in port. Commercial vessels
should prepare for rough seas and consider remaining in port
until hazardous seas subside.

NWSheadline: HAZARDOUS SEAS WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM PST THURSDAY... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
